  **4**       Defect Resolution  Eliminate defects        Layer 1 deployment
              & Prioritized      through prioritized      process, Layer 2
              Backlog Process    resolution with verified verification, Layer 3
                                 closure.                 SLAs, Layer 5 lifecycle

