              Taxonomy & Metrics classification           layers. Authoritative
              Reference          vocabulary and metrics   for terminology.
                                 definitions used by all  
                                 layers.                  
  ----------- ------------------ ------------------------ -----------------------

> *The five layers form a closed loop: Prevention reduces defects.
> Testing catches what prevention misses. The dashboard makes defects
> visible. Resolution eliminates them. The taxonomy ensures everyone is
> speaking the same language. Each defect resolved feeds back into
> prevention through root cause analysis, regression tests, and process
> improvement.*

